This paper is primarily focused on improving the resiliency of data centers, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the correlation between network traffic and power consumption, which is related to Networked Systems (cs.NI) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of monitoring critical applications and handling failures, which is related to Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
